MESSAGE.value: Generate edgeR up to the point where we estimate dispersion.
Now produce results in an R table, but not connected to concept output table yet.
Fix generation of - binary operator.
Put the output in the destination table.
Improve TableRef scope.
Add write table concept to export a table to tab/csv format.
Remove info statement from scope calculation.
Do not write row.names with write.table. Do not cluster when building heatmap.
Tweak constrainsts and error rules for FutureTable.
Add intention to transfer groups from one table to another.
Heatmap: add the ability to select more than one group.

Refactor heatmap generation to make it compatible with multiplot (heatmap now renders inside a function called plot_..). This makes it possible to use heatmaps in multiplot or also render them to PDF.
Fix legend for heatmap.
Add a new way to specify annotations for heatmap. Use the intention add/remove annotations to enable/disable.

Use common dispersion before tagwise, trended dispersion does not seem too stable. heatmap: do not sort sample columns, this disrupts the order by group usage that is now determined by heatmap annotations.
Add ability to specify pdf witdh and height in inspector under render to PDF.
Add ability to include histograms in a multiplot.
Add ColorPlotStyle to tables language. Reference the new style from BoxPlot and Histogram. Add metaR.configuration solution with default colorful and gray palettes.
Add editor.images language with a refreshable image concept.
Add Image to editor.images language.
Use auto-refreshable image in multiplot.
Commit project files before branching.
Apply typed columns migration script.
Test loading a typed table.
